_sText:
A simple map to battle on. 
you start with a scout equiped and you can shoot the opposing team by shooting through the holes.
on the left of the spawn you can choose to enter the hallways and get a m4a1 equiped. 
50 seconds after the start of each round a button will be available to both teams. This button will break the wall that defends the opposing team so that they will be more vulnerable.
